---

<section class="relative min-h-screen w-full flex items-end overflow-hidden">
  <img
    src="/images/fighter-jets.jpg"
    alt="Fighter jets in formation"
    class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
  />
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 via-black/40 to-black/10"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-14 pb-16 sm:pb-24">
    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-7xl font-display text-white leading-[1.1] mb-8 max-w-4xl">
      Developing the Next Generation of National Security Innovators
    </h1>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mb-10">
      <p class="text-white/70 leading-relaxed text-base md:text-lg">
        San Jose State sits at the center of Silicon Valley, surrounded by the companies and technologies reshaping national defense. The talent is here. What's been missing is the pipeline connecting that talent to the missions that need it most. NSIN at SJSU was founded to close that gap.
      </p>
      <p class="text-white/70 leading-relaxed text-base md:text-lg">
        We bring together students from engineering, computer science, policy, and business to work on the problems our country can't afford to ignore. Supply chain vulnerabilities, emerging threats, critical infrastructure, strategic competition. These challenges demand people from every discipline working together, and we're building that team at SJSU.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="border-l-2 border-white/30 pl-6 max-w-2xl">
      <p class="font-display text-lg md:text-xl text-white/80 leading-relaxed italic">
        "What would it look like to take those bright people out of the search engine optimization industry, out of the augmented reality mustache emoji industry, and put them to work on things that were more important."
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-white/40 text-sm">
        Palmer Luckey, founder of Anduril Industries
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
